  "description": "<h3>Job Description</h3><p>Set up, preperation and operation of welding equipment</p><p>Familiarity with different materials including aluminium, stainless steel and mild steel</p><p>Ability to read technical drawings</p><p>Capability to fabricate, assemble and fit parts together</p><p>Other duties as required by management</p><h3>Job Requirements</h3><p>Experience in Welding for 2 years and above</p><p>Good fitness</p><p>Able to work with minimal supervision</p><p>Knowledge of MIG, ARC & TIG welding</p><p>Able to work on weekends and public holidays</p><p>Able to work at night shift and split shift</p>",
