  "hiringCompany": {
    "uen": "199101680M",
    "description": "<p>\r\n\tYEO ENG KOON (S) PTE LTD started as a LPG distributor more than 40 years ago. With our customers mainly from the F&B industry, we saw the need to value-add to our existing gas supply business. Hence, the one-stop kitchen resource concept was hatched to facilitate customers in their kitchen renovations and equipment needs. As a one-stop kitchen resource, we offer customers a cost-effective and time-saving solution through the products and services that we provide. Customers looking to renovate their kitchen or replace their kitchen equipment can consult our professionally trained sales team on kitchen layout, kitchen equipment , kitchen exhaust system, fire suppression system and gas supply. Customers can enjoy a hassle-free kitchen make-over experience by entrusting the co-ordination to us. For after-sales service, our pool of trained technicians are at hand to trouble-shoot and provide repair and maintenance services. Our motto of placing customer’s need above ourselves is the driving force behind our constant and relentless pursuit of re-inventing ourselves through cost and energy efficient products and services that give savings to customers. Our customer’s business is our business!</p>\r\n",
